## Real-World Applications

This project uses IPL as a demo, but **the same architecture works on any structured dataset**:

| Domain | Example Question |
|--------|-----------------|
| **E-commerce** | "Top 10 products by return rate in 2024?" |
| **Finance** | "Show monthly revenue trend for Q3 vs Q4" |
| **Healthcare** | "Which treatment has the highest recovery rate?" |
| **HR Analytics** | "Attrition rate by department last 2 years?" |
| **Marketing** | "Top campaigns by ROI this quarter?" |

**Why it matters:** Democratizes data access — non-technical teams get self-serve analytics without depending on data engineers for every query.

---

## Safety

- Read-only query enforcement (blocks DROP, DELETE, UPDATE, INSERT)
- Schema-grounded prompting reduces LLM hallucinations
- Error handling for malformed SQL — shown cleanly in UI, never crashes

